Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.14,2:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}去捍卫 世间的平凡
Dialogue: 0,2:06:45.31,2:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}一身胆 去挑战 漫漫黑暗
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.56,2:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}驱散所有的严寒
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.52,2:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}去点燃 无尽的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.81,2:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}去捍卫 每份浪漫
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.89,2:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}每张脸 每一个小小的缘
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.14,2:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}十万难 无法阻拦
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.14,2:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶书_GBK\c&HF69AC8&\fs80}我勇敢 放飞心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,天地间爆发了一场大劫难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,生灵涂炭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,纷争撕杀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最终
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,商周决战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人神合力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,共渡劫难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,定立了封神榜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,自此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,众神归位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,各造一方洞府
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,世间重归太平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最后半桶混元气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷 再不开张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咱这船就开不动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我说二爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没开张了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这得挣钱买气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老姚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,从前大家都能腾云驾雾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可就那场天灾之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这长翅膀的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,神仙妖怪们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就只能这么驾着船飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那场天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候的事来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我都忘了从前怎么飞的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这听着就跟传说里的事似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,告示板有新活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蓬莱神府发的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,终于转运了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就在蓬莱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这活不能被别的赏银捕手给抢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么才二十贯三界通宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这看着也是个狠角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,蓬莱神府也穷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再不开张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要断顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那咱们去碰碰运气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,斯晨时已届兮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,朱雀门开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,逍遥而大同兮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,唯我蓬莱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,万方之神灵兮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,稳载云气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,各得安其所兮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,各行其道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要求仙丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,掏钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要么滚蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,假药吃不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,吃不起就滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一个神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这组合 挺厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,落魄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么组都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,落魄神仙不如狗没听过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我那狗活得就比我舒坦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你看又蹭我一身味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,二十贯钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为 是那处洞山的捕快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是个赏银捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀!疼疼疼 头还挺硬啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你跑什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要钱又不要命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你小心摔着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妙 这时候没气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想逮我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是嘛玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来的正巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它那鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你又不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这闻着你身上味就追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这都什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,伤风败俗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是 羡慕嫉妒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干这 不就为钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你们五倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一百贯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就你这假药贩子德行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谁信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就埋在桥边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这听着不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你问问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这又是嘛呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,问下天地万物乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是放还 是不放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,二十贯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就刚才那口琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是面朝上放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还是面朝下放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你先前也没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有钱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有人找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有送上门的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对 而且还是个大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,登门拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你是木二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,姓木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,排行第二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,木二就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是赏银捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抓人 不找人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你帮我抓一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那正是在下的业务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他偷了一件宝物 我姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么宝物?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一琢磨事就头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,头疼 那就别告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来一杯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我姐姐 从小相依为命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,十二年前那场三界大灾祸后 她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只给我留下了那件宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家的传家宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都行 都的收费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么多都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是万物如意盏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,它能收纳这世间别的器物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不能收纳的一切物品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他偷了这宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,逃去了方壶仙岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你找的这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他得有个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你听过?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这名字少见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小女婉罗 在瀛洲静候消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有来历
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看她这身衣袍 这条船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这气质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可是她为什么找我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们除了便宜 也没什么优势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为期十五日兮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,售馨即止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,上品混元气兮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,助君畅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,寅字口 收讫三袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,捧完那边哪个气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,丁字口 三袋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为期十五日兮 售馨即止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上品混元气兮 助君畅行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你挡着我道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别打了 别打了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别打了 快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-听见没有 -去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,何人滋事 禁止斗殴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 好大的胆子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老实点都别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,老大 天兵来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谁放的狼烟?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们几个 跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老大...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,站住...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快开船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,设置已毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,前方到站方壶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,预计抵达 戌时(晚间19-21点)三刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,请君坐稳扶好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,祝君平安翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,客官 恭迎大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,里边请
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,滚 输光了还玩个屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,买定离手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷 您来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,何发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爷有什么吩咐?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,问你点事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟豁! 我这耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,听力已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再不行 你也还是顺风耳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看在我之前欠您的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,您要问我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,找个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,叫沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,三位好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不意偶遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么粗鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瞎啦 真瞎啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,木二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,赏银捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我说木木 不不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,木哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就你那三尖两刃刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你那个弹弓银弹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这位就是大名鼎鼎的杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是二郎真君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 这么落魄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么这么落魄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,别别 我来替你说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,话说十二年前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬因为杨婵三圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要和凡人私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,犯了天条
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就将其镇在了华山之下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是他的亲妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杨婵在被镇到山下之前 奋力反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用华山的至宝 宝莲灯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伤了他的天眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:23:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,废了他的神功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:24:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,从此他的元神 就再也出不来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,会为了一个什么破天条
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把自己的亲妹妹镇在华山之下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,害得人家 家破人亡妻离子散
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当年你擒拿我们三兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多威风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今天...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我可得好好的揍你一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.35,0:24:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,接着玩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.60,0:24:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,魔家兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.10,0:24:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,魔礼红 魔礼海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 没想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.26,0:25:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天 你竟然沦落到要我来出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.18,0:25:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,自从十二年前华山那会一次后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.06,0:25:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就再也没有你的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.93,0:25:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然当了个赏银捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.43,0:25:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我总得吃饭呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.14,0:25:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才在角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.89,0:25:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我听你要找一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.26,0:25:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有份赏银
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.26,0:25:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别找他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是为他而来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.81,0:25:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你万万不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.60,0:25:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,否则...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.06,0:25:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然敢威胁杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.56,0:25:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 你可真的不是当年的二郎神了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.56,0:25:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了二位
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.56,0:25:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.06,0:26:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.85,0:26:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看你往哪跑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.06,0:26:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,终于有我追的你上天无门的这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.43,0:26:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,海老大 这些是您找的新帮手?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.51,0:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老弟兄们 都被你害死在了哪条船上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.89,0:26:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,把东西交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.39,0:26:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己下了船舱偷的那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.93,0:26:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谁告诉你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.27,0:26:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.39,0:26:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我找的海老大
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.43,0:26:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,海老大 新宠物啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.60,0:27:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那条船上最宝贵的...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.76,0:27:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你偷走的那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.81,0:27:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.10,0:27:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我就要你一条胳膊 一条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.72,0:27:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,瞎了眼的 别凑这个热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.93,0:27:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,借过
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.26,0:27:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,海老大你有帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.56,0:27:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.68,0:27:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西你先收着 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.39,0:27:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,误会 误会
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.18,0:27:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天一起要了你们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.01,0:27:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他真没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.68,0:27:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.60,0:28:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢相助
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.81,0:28:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,等我事成 一定涌泉相报
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你下手未免也太狠了点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我落在他们手里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.60,0:28:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那下场比死还惨十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.01,0:28:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.18,0:28:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你方才还真的把你这宝贝塞给我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.35,0:28:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不塞给你 他们怎么相信你是我帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.10,0:28:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不怕我不还你?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.52,0:28:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.26,0:28:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,口气不小
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.01,0:28:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.51,0:28:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是谁 我都会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.93,0:29:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是梅山杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.76,0:29:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.06,0:29:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.93,0:29:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有人委托我来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.26,0:29:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 怎么又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.76,0:29:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么又是你们两兄弟?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.93,0:29:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.26,0:29:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我先说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.68,0:29:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是路过碰到了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.06,0:29:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,礼守首所杀不是杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.06,0:29:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.89,0:29:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才逃走那人就是你要找的沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.72,0:29:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 这么巧?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.26,0:30:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一个小毛贼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.89,0:30:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,至于这么 兴师动众?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不知道沉香是何人?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.51,0:30:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他出自你的师门
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.89,0:30:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的师侄
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.51,0:30:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,既然今日你已身在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.22,0:30:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他的来历
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.39,0:30:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你去问问你的师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.31,0:30:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,玉鼎真人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.22,0:31:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,施主 你好厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.51,0:31:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,烦请禀上师尊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.26,0:31:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,徒儿杨戬求见
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.93,0:31:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,杨师伯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.18,0:31:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,师伯快随我来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.85,0:32:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿 你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.93,0:32:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛还没有好转
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.06,0:32:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.89,0:32:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如此厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.26,0:32:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,尽力也只能勉强睁开一缝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.06,0:32:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但眼前只有极亮的金光乱异
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.77,0:32:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不能见一物
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.27,0:32:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,难解
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.64,0:32:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.97,0:32:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可以借极强的外力 去冲开这层屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.76,0:32:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但只怕 会伤上加伤
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.35,0:32:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.14,0:32:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你自小如我门下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我视你如子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.56,0:33:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,十二年前
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.60,0:33:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你将莲花峰封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.89,0:33:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可是灾祸连连
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.97,0:33:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,神界日渐衰落
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.06,0:33:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,妖魔鬼怪纷纷而起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.81,0:33:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.18,0:33:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,万物苍生终究要再受一击
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.22,0:33:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,师傅您的四字教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,尽力而为
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.89,0:33:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.51,0:33:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尽力而为
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.81,0:33:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为了正道长驻
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.10,0:33:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎能不勉力补天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.18,0:33:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,弟子明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.72,0:33:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.06,0:33:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我在山下遇见了一位少年
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.39,0:34:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说是出于我师门下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.43,0:34:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,名叫沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.56,0:34:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.89,0:34:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你送上山的好外甥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.06,0:34:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,此事 你确实不知
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.72,0:34:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你送他上山时
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.06,0:34:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是个哇哇啼哭的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.56,0:34:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这些年你从没见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.76,0:34:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我给它取名沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.39,0:34:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,望他能心如沉香木一般 安神 收敛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.89,0:34:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎知他...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.56,0:34:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我门下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.43,0:34:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,居然出了一个杀师的逆徒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.93,0:34:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,陪你大师兄去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.89,0:34:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,师父将二师兄的法身封印
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.18,0:34:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,以待有日尸解
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.76,0:35:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香为何会做这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.35,0:35:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就看出
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.60,0:35:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一个天生反骨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.76,0:35:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不服管教的孽障
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.60,0:35:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不过师傅念你莲花峰一事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.39,0:35:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不愿赶他下山
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.68,0:35:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只是让二师兄收他为徒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.76,0:35:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对他好生管教
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.60,0:35:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,二师弟脾气暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.56,0:35:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他被什么所伤?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.06,0:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他和申公豹联手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.93,0:35:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,趁二师兄不备害死了他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.14,0:35:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,申公豹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.89,0:35:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他又现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.43,0:35:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.39,0:35:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知这小子是如何认识申公豹的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.22,0:35:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,申公豹的分身术 确实非同小可
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.76,0:35:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还盗走了二师兄新近炼成的法宝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.76,0:35:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么法宝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.76,0:35:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,万物如意盏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.22,0:36:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.43,0:36:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.76,0:36:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有了宝莲灯的灯油
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.81,0:36:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,下一步当然是拿宝莲灯的灯罩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.56,0:36:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇到了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.56,0:36:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.56,0:36:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 我的同门师伯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.10,0:36:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.39,0:36:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他在找我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.93,0:36:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你师父
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.18,0:36:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.22,0:36:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他似乎不知此事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.77,0:37:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.76,0:37:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.93,0:37:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来 来 来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.26,0:37:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你只知道杨戬是你师伯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.06,0:37:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他是你亲舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.47,0:37:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我舅舅?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.56,0:37:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也是他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.89,0:37:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,亲手将你母亲镇在了莲花峰下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.26,0:37:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬的法力 自然是强的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,宝莲灯也被他的力量反击 碎作了几块
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.93,0:37:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只要找齐这些碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.39,0:37:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,宝莲灯复原如初
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.72,0:37:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能借宝莲灯之力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.72,0:37:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,劈开花莲峰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.89,0:37:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,救出你母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.18,0:38:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 你师父
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.35,0:38:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你师尊一门
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.06,0:38:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,都是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.60,0:38:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.60,0:38:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我申公豹 封了个分水将军的名号
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.93,0:38:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,却把我塞进了东海海眼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.10,0:38:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,满口仁义道德
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.56,0:38:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,实则虚伪透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.97,0:38:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我就咬着牙忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.43,0:38:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.52,0:38:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,报仇的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.18,0:38:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,终于被我等到了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.56,0:39:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 他为什么要找我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.26,0:39:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,自然还是为了宝莲灯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.56,0:39:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那宝莲灯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.60,0:39:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你母亲的一脉血亲才能运用
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.31,0:39:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.18,0:39:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还盗走了二师兄新近炼成的法宝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.10,0:39:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,万物如意盏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.60,0:39:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他偷了一件宝物 我姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.93,0:39:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是万物如意盏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.26,0:39:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,小女婉罗在瀛洲静候消息
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.06,0:40:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,开场了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.68,0:40:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这混元气 真能让人飞起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.51,0:40:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妙哉 妙哉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.97,0:42:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-哎呀!  -是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.85,0:42:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这丝竹交错无鼓自鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.77,0:42:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妙哉 妙哉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.43,0:42:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,来人 沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.47,0:42:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.76,0:43:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,二郎 这么进来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.22,0:43:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.26,0:43:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.64,0:43:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才一路走来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.39,0:43:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,听婉罗姑娘曼舞轻歌
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.56,0:43:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉忘形 唐突了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.77,0:43:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢 听我的曲儿
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.85,0:43:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,天外之音
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.35,0:43:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,余音绕梁
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.89,0:43:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜曹子建这洛神赋
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.56,0:43:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,却是伤心词
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.93,0:43:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这难言之痛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.68,0:43:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,思念之苦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.52,0:43:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是惆怅
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.35,0:43:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,二郎怎么呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.89,0:44:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.60,0:44:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上一次见到姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.26,0:44:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就觉得姑娘似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.76,0:44:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,却不知在何处见过
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.60,0:44:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是二郎的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.85,0:44:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也许...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.89,0:44:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.85,0:44:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那梦中之人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.85,0:44:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也许...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.26,0:44:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.68,0:44:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小贼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.76,0:44:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.39,0:44:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他又逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.26,0:44:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香出自我师门
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.26,0:44:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的师侄
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.35,0:44:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你 木二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.77,0:44:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,鄙姓杨 单名戬
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.76,0:44:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.60,0:44:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那只万物如意盏
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.18,0:44:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是沉香的师父所炼得法宝
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.06,0:44:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想请教姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.51,0:44:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为何要谎称那如意盏
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.01,0:45:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是你姐姐之物?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.39,0:45:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.68,0:45:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有些事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.43,0:45:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不要知道为好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.31,0:45:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.06,0:45:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.39,0:45:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.81,0:45:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-母亲 母亲... -戬儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.01,0:45:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,劈开山
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.85,0:45:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.93,0:45:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,劈开山
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.85,0:45:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.39,0:45:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.68,0:46:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,方壶 废弃船坞寻沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.10,0:47:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这防身招式不错
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.01,0:47:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就是下手狠了点
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.51,0:47:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.22,0:47:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去找宝莲灯?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.26,0:47:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,关你什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.76,0:47:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你已经知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.26,0:47:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.77,0:47:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.77,0:47:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是我把你送去的金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.93,0:47:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那时你刚出生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.64,0:47:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,名字都还没来得及取
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.85,0:47:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只有...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.47,0:48:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只有 这没一丁点大
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.18,0:48:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我那个师弟
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.85,0:48:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他脾气暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.43,0:48:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道师父为什么要把你交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.18,0:48:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里过得不好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.39,0:48:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.93,0:48:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也不过每天什么都不教我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.35,0:48:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,每天打我一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.85,0:48:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,饿饿肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.31,0:48:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说我是个没爹没娘的贱种
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.43,0:48:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.06,0:48:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但就算是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.43,0:48:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不能要了他的命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.56,0:48:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也不该将我母亲压在莲花峰下
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.22,0:48:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.97,0:48:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈...杨戬...干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.89,0:48:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香你戕害同门 欺师灭祖
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.14,0:48:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现奉命将你擒拿
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.76,0:48:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.56,0:48:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还不束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.76,0:49:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 这次我们亲眼所见
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.72,0:49:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是你放走了他
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.31,0:49:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只能将你拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.22,0:49:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不用麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.76,0:49:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等我手头这单活忙完了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.43,0:49:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我绑好自己登门自首
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.56,0:50:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,唉!杨戬 得罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.60,0:50:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,烽火齐动
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.93,0:50:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,缚神弦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.06,0:51:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们老四也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.01,0:51:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这么 啊 偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.60,0:51:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可不像你们兄弟风格
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.76,0:51:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,上回封神之战
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.76,0:51:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你打败我们四兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.76,0:51:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,用的手段不也是偷偷摸摸的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.43,0:51:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.60,0:51:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 我一直劝他们
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.97,0:51:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,说这事不会是你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.10,0:51:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.10,0:51:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,此事你认个罪
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.43,0:51:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有什么难处
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.39,0:51:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会替你向天庭分解的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.06,0:51:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是...我做了什么事了我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.39,0:51:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.56,0:51:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你与沉香同谋
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.10,0:51:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,欺师灭祖戕害同门的事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.43,0:51:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.72,0:51:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.47,0:51:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哎唷...疼疼疼疼疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.18,0:52:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,新来的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.39,0:52:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,弄么大动静 干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.39,0:52:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你头回进监狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.14,0:52:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.22,0:52:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 哟 哟 这不杨戬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.68,0:52:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪位啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.14,0:52:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我 不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.72,0:52:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀! 你 你 你 唉！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.39,0:52:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,葫芦 仙丹
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.10,0:52:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大高个 我旁边有个大高个
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.85,0:52:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩Duang 然后你疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.93,0:52:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我嘟嘟嘟 呲
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.18,0:52:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在后面 刷刷刷
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.76,0:52:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你后来
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.72,0:52:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,二十贯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.01,0:52:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别看你是杨戬
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.06,0:52:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在我眼里 呸! 狗屁都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.93,0:52:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不给孝敬钱 一样杀威棒伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.64,0:52:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,, 大哥 慢走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.18,0:53:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-留神 -瞎叫唤什么
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.60,0:53:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 虽然是我把你抓
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.39,0:53:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我抓进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.10,0:53:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可也算不上嘛生死仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.76,0:53:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我大度
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.56,0:53:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样对
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.14,0:53:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样对牢卒不理不睬的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.89,0:53:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小心他回头给你上手段
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.76,0:53:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你听见没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.56,0:54:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,打起来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.93,0:54:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这下有
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.26,0:54:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这下有好戏看了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.85,0:54:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,难道有人要劫狱?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.56,0:54:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬你不看啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.68,0:54:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不会是来 救你的 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.43,0:54:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.68,0:54:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,给我老实点 别给我惹麻烦！听明白没?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.60,0:54:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.60,0:54:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,走啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.35,0:55:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.51,0:55:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你这葫芦里 到底卖的什么药啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.43,0:55:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 重要的...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.89,0:55:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是 咱们下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.14,0:55:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哮天 二爷呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.77,0:55:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.35,0:55:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.10,0:55:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 你管管我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.68,0:56:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.22,0:56:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.43,0:56:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,从梅山独领一方的幕府
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.89,0:56:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到游荡四方的赏银捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.56,0:56:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再成了蓬莱的逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.85,0:56:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.68,0:56:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.68,0:56:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,混的可是越来越差了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.39,0:56:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可是快意自在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.97,0:56:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 自在 - 自在...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.72,0:57:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哮天...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.01,0:57:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.89,0:57:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,二郎 我们接下来要去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.56,0:57:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那灯罩就在那塔中
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.06,0:57:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那几道光 就是灯罩发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.43,0:57:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这灯罩不知被谁找到
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.26,0:57:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用作了导航的号灯
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.76,0:58:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,非得喝这么多酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.26,0:58:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天地一朝
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.89,0:58:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,万朝须臾
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.93,0:58:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,唯酒是务
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.27,0:58:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,焉知其余
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.72,0:58:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,增长天王
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.68,0:58:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.56,0:58:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,守候多时
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.39,0:58:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,幸会....
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.06,0:58:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这位就是沉香
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.26,0:58:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,杀师逃徒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.22,0:59:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,增长天王
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.43,0:59:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你自然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.10,0:59:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那群玄鸟 迟早是要飞出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.43,0:59:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们魔家兄弟不想见到那一方天地
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.56,0:59:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从此大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.76,0:59:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可那群玄鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.39,0:59:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,又如何能长久的被镇住呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.56,0:59:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这座华山
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.10,0:59:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然如今看着摇摇欲坠
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.56,0:59:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当初可是我们舍命才将玄鸟镇住的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.43,0:59:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,能多镇住一日
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.39,0:59:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就多镇一日
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.26,0:59:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,魔礼青
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.89,0:59:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那这次...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.60,0:59:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你我就 是敌非友了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.60,1:01:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还动真格的了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.22,1:02:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,分身术
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.14,1:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会分身术?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.43,1:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小小年纪
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.68,1:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然学了申公豹的邪术
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.43,1:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,练成了元神
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.47,1:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能赢 都行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.26,1:03:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,傻小子 快跑!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.18,1:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.97,1:05:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.02,1:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快走...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.85,1:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,师兄...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.56,1:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,又见面了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.26,1:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你风采依旧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.89,1:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,申公豹
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.22,1:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.64,1:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多年不见
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.06,1:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,听说 你落魄的很
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.10,1:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天眼都瞎了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.93,1:08:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜了当年劈开桃山的小杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.26,1:08:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那个杨戬 我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.89,1:08:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,申公豹 沉香呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.85,1:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他自己逃了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.35,1:08:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是个心狠手辣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.76,1:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,像我年轻的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.76,1:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的衣钵传人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.39,1:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你可知沉香去了何处?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.06,1:08:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他那点小秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.47,1:08:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,梅山 渡月池
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.06,1:09:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你这伤...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.56,1:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.56,1:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,人生如剑 夺有何为
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.81,1:09:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,践我孤乐 岁月如驰
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.72,1:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这靠谱吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.51,1:10:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,妥了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.85,1:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛事没有 我偷渡过几回
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.14,1:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,安全的很
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.60,1:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟只是偷渡的小器械
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.43,1:10:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只能送他一人过去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.72,1:11:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.18,1:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 那翁说了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.85,1:11:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的时候 有点晃啊!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.18,1:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.72,1:11:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,人间 长安
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.43,1:12:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是长安
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.01,1:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,人间正在战争
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.81,1:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你来啦！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.01,1:13:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,新的灯盏
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.06,1:13:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,灯油
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.89,1:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老的灯罩
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.60,1:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,宝莲灯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.06,1:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这...这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.97,1:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.76,1:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,既然来了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.93,1:14:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,别藏了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.26,1:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你来告诉沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.60,1:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这宝莲灯的真正用途吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.56,1:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.93,1:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,华山的莲花峰下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.76,1:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,镇住了一群玄鸟
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.10,1:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是万火之源 有毁天灾的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.51,1:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦爆发天地崩裂
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.60,1:14:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,女娲娘娘给了你母亲这盏宝莲灯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.26,1:14:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,让她日日夜夜守在莲花峰上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.01,1:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但十二年前
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.51,1:14:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,玄鸟们躁动不安
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.06,1:14:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宝莲灯眼看就要镇不住他们
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.01,1:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我受师父之命去助你母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.35,1:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但玄鸟之力太过猛烈
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.56,1:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,宝莲灯碎了...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.06,1:15:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,最后时刻
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.35,1:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲跳下莲花峰
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.10,1:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,试图用自己的身体挡住玄鸟
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.52,1:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 孩子就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.68,1:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.39,1:15:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要守住莲花峰
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.85,1:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒转斧柄插入石中
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.68,1:15:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,终于 镇住了玄鸟
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.14,1:15:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的天眼...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.56,1:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从此睁不开了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.72,1:16:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我母亲封在了莲花峰下
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.35,1:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因为她嫁了个凡人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.56,1:16:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.14,1:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲也一样嫁给了一个凡人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.85,1:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,生下了我和你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.72,1:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我身负重伤 无力照顾你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.89,1:16:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就将你送去了金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.27,1:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为何从没有来看过我?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.35,1:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我舅舅
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.56,1:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,师父说你成年之前不准我探视
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.56,1:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的是真的吗? 婉姥姥
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.77,1:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,婉姥姥?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.39,1:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是 他说的 是真的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.06,1:16:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.43,1:16:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲瑶姬 是我的好姐妹
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.18,1:16:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有个名号 巫山神女
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.85,1:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这些事的来龙去脉不止于此
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.35,1:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,随我来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.18,1:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,华山
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.35,1:17:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是莲花峰
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.72,1:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那几道光
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.06,1:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是被镇压在峰底的玄鸟
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.60,1:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在躁动不安
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.60,1:17:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲 她就被压在那座山下
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.89,1:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这离山的烽火台
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.14,1:17:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,都说周幽王为了博褒姒一笑
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.56,1:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,烽火戏诸侯
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.68,1:17:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.22,1:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,身死国灭
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.85,1:17:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都是女人的错
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.10,1:17:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.68,1:17:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么要用宝莲灯
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.72,1:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来镇住玄鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.26,1:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.56,1:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当初你师父镇住玄鸟
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.47,1:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,借吸取玄鸟之力
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.89,1:18:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,才得以建成金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.43,1:18:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,玄鸟脱身
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.51,1:18:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,金霞洞会就此坍塌
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.51,1:18:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,镇住玄鸟 维持金霞洞不倒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.97,1:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是你师父让你镇住玄鸟的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.18,1:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,师父只告诉我
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.76,1:18:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,镇住玄鸟 就能拯救苍生
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.56,1:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,挡住大劫
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.76,1:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有告诉我 这和金霞洞有关
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.85,1:18:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你师父只为自己
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.22,1:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,万物总要循环 玄鸟终得飞起
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.43,1:18:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,镇得住吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.56,1:18:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 还记得你劈开桃山
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.26,1:18:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么时候吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.35,1:18:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我劈开桃山?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.76,1:18:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上一次的大劫
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.93,1:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你师父
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.68,1:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只是了 保他金霞洞的那一方势力
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.76,1:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你师父骗了你
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.06,1:19:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们劈开华山
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.39,1:19:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,救出杨婵
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.72,1:19:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,婉罗姑娘 就算您说的确有其事
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.51,1:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但如此大事
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.89,1:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我得带您去见师父
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.39,1:19:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当面对质
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.76,1:19:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.06,1:19:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.39,1:19:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谁要跟你一起去?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.27,1:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟山上那些人都一样
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.43,1:19:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不去
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.10,1:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己去
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.43,1:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.56,1:19:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今 你还要去找你师父
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.02,1:21:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,巫山神女
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.68,1:21:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只怕沉香和你一起
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.85,1:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,会落个申公豹的下场
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.14,1:21:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你何出此言?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.06,1:21:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,瀛洲仙乐坊那次
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.26,1:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我被迷倒入梦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.43,1:21:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,梦中母亲叮嘱我去劈山
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.52,1:21:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿 劈开山...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.93,1:21:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那人其实不是我母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.10,1:21:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而是您
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.56,1:21:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,巫山神女
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.01,1:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,梦中颠倒迷惑众生
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.26,1:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,正是您的手段
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.06,1:21:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香的师父
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.31,1:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是沉香所害
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.52,1:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可也不是申公豹
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.22,1:21:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我师弟身上的伤
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.76,1:21:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是一片丝网模样
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.56,1:21:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到申公豹时
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.06,1:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.06,1:21:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他先是被一种厉害的法宝所伤
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.10,1:21:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但真正致命的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.89,1:21:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,同样是丝网伤口
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.35,1:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就在方才
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.56,1:21:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,您情急之下施展出的绫罗网
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.85,1:22:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而那一片丝网
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.60,1:22:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,正是您的独门法术
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.60,1:22:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香的师父
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.85,1:22:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有申公豹
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.93,1:22:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都是您杀的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.68,1:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.64,1:22:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.64,1:22:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.72,1:22:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么 要杀他们
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.51,1:22:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你师父不死
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.06,1:22:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会离开金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.76,1:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,申公豹倒是可惜
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.39,1:22:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们商定携手行事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.68,1:22:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎料他受了那等重伤
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.39,1:22:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,生不如死
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.31,1:22:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只好助他了结
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.06,1:22:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,您为什么要这样做?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.18,1:22:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香我做了这些事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.10,1:22:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都是为了劈开山
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.51,1:22:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,救出你母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.60,1:22:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪像你
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.56,1:22:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但无论如何
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.97,1:22:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不能杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.68,1:23:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,住手...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.06,1:24:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.51,1:24:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.27,1:24:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它太热了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.43,1:24:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你解下来了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.60,1:24:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它一直就在我的手腕上
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.60,1:24:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都取不下来
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.72,1:24:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.76,1:24:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也许
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.72,1:24:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是你血脉相连的舅舅
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.60,1:25:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你母亲用他的头发编的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.89,1:25:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她跳下莲花峰前
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.06,1:25:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让我把这发绳给你
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.43,1:25:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这发绳是一支灯芯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.14,1:25:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,点亮宝莲灯的灯芯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.72,1:25:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很想母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.18,1:25:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去华山吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.85,1:25:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个事情弄个水落石出
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.02,1:26:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,九转玄功
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.72,1:28:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我家
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.72,1:29:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.64,1:29:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.89,1:30:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是封神榜上的人物
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.01,1:30:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是我熟视无睹了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.26,1:30:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这华山之上
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.64,1:30:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,居然真的有个封神榜
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.06,1:31:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的劈山斧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.01,1:31:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,它封住的是你劈下的山头
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.39,1:31:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没完全封住
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.06,1:31:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这透出的玄鸟之力
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.72,1:31:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看见了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.10,1:31:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.43,1:31:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.27,1:32:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,捆仙索
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.43,1:32:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香 快退
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.31,1:32:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舅舅
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.97,1:32:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,终于抓住了你这逆徒
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.72,1:32:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这太极图是何等宝贝
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.64,1:33:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,心想何物 何物变现
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.93,1:33:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,心虑百事 百事即至
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.89,1:33:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也只有这太极图
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.43,1:33:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,能困住杨戬了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.22,1:33:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.27,1:33:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.56,1:33:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.93,1:33:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.85,1:33:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,劈开山
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.47,1:34:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.35,1:34:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.97,1:34:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-戬儿... -母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.39,1:34:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,桃山已开
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.60,1:34:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我也该去了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.68,1:34:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.93,1:34:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,命运如此
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.51,1:34:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家女人的命
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.43,1:34:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是镇住山
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.85,1:34:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,守护世间太平
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.93,1:34:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.27,1:34:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.56,1:35:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,无需哭泣
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.10,1:35:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.18,1:35:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这点点星火
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.76,1:35:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.72,1:35:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,万物生生不息
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.26,1:35:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我就活在这天地万物中...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.51,1:35:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.35,1:35:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想我了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.22,1:35:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你便看那世间万家灯火
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.76,1:35:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就看到了我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.68,1:35:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.97,1:35:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.89,1:35:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经劈开桃山了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.51,1:35:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.06,1:35:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,镇住华山
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.81,1:35:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,镇住华山
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.39,1:35:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,世间安宁
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.35,1:35:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,镇住华山
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.10,1:35:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,世间安宁
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.22,1:35:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.72,1:35:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-孩子就拜托你了 -妹妹
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.89,1:36:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛 还没有好转
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.06,1:36:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.35,1:36:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,十二年前
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.39,1:36:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你将莲花峰封住了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.27,1:36:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.43,1:36:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,灾祸连连
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.10,1:36:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我错了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.68,1:36:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,万物苍生 终究要再受一劫
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.68,1:36:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.01,1:36:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为了正道常驻
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.60,1:37:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎能不勉力补天呢
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.39,1:37:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.77,1:37:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是太极图
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.35,1:37:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是您把我困在了太极图中
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.14,1:37:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我了不起的徒儿
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.85,1:37:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然能让太极图凡人幻象慢慢降下来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.76,1:37:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.06,1:38:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得太极图
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.39,1:38:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得殷洪被他的师父
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.60,1:38:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在太极图中化成了飞灰
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.01,1:38:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,师父我犯了什么大罪?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.31,1:38:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.68,1:38:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让沉香劈开华山
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.64,1:38:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切果然都是因为金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.56,1:38:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.72,1:38:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,金霞洞绝不能倒
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.72,1:38:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我费尽心血
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.31,1:38:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了不让这金霞洞 一夕坍塌
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.47,1:38:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.26,1:38:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,杨婵镇在了华山之下
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.06,1:38:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是她的命
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.31,1:38:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.26,1:38:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.01,1:38:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们杨家一脉
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.10,1:38:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,母与子
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.56,1:38:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,生来就与这动摇天地的大劫难有有关
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.60,1:38:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为保世间太平
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.18,1:39:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲们镇住了山
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.26,1:39:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而那儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.68,1:39:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为解救母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.56,1:39:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要去奋力劈山
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.60,1:39:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不知
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.93,1:39:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把山劈开
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.01,1:39:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,玄鸟出 金霞洞塌
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.76,1:39:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,带来的是大劫降临 世间大乱
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.01,1:39:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,直到渡过大劫
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.68,1:39:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,世间才能又一次安定
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.18,1:39:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.22,1:39:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,上一回劈山 是你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.06,1:39:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这一回 轮到了沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.35,1:39:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.93,1:39:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当年我无父无母
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.43,1:40:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,您收我为徒 抚养我长大
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.51,1:40:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,教我种种玄功法术
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.51,1:40:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是利用我好让我有一日
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.76,1:40:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有力量去劈开桃山
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.76,1:40:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而您收沉香入门下
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.22,1:40:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不教玄功 不告诉他身世 让他懵懂无知
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.60,1:40:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是欺瞒他让他不能去劈开华山
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.81,1:40:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.56,1:40:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.76,1:40:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你母亲一样
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.01,1:40:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,都是要保这世间太平
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.93,1:40:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要玄鸟还多镇在山底一时
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.89,1:40:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,金霞洞就能多维持一刻
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.93,1:40:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的金霞洞早就维持不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.43,1:40:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,玄鸟压制越久
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.14,1:40:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,威力越大
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.35,1:40:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一日爆发而出
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.35,1:40:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你保你的金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.14,1:40:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,根本无关灾难
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.72,1:40:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只为保护你自己
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.52,1:40:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.18,1:40:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我等一生心血所结
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.18,1:40:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一荣俱荣
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.85,1:41:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一损俱损
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.51,1:41:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就算错
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.76,1:41:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也只能错到底
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.60,1:41:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.35,1:41:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我原来只是你的一枚棋子
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.85,1:41:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,戬儿
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.01,1:41:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.26,1:41:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能将你们一起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.18,1:41:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,用太极图化了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.26,1:42:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,捆仙索 太极图
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.06,1:42:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我从你师伯师叔们那借来的法宝
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.43,1:42:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所谋相同
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.06,1:42:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,世间不能再乱了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.85,1:42:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.39,1:42:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.22,1:42:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,宝莲灯护体
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.18,1:43:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,宝莲灯
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.06,1:43:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,九转玄功
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.93,1:43:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,进步不小
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.85,1:44:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,玄鸟之力 好生厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.89,1:44:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,竟能划破太极图
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.39,1:45:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,舅舅...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.14,1:45:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他借玄鸟之力
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.60,1:45:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,冲开了天眼
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.43,1:46:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.14,1:46:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要一错到底
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.10,1:46:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,法天象地
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.72,1:46:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.56,1:47:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快拦住他
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.68,1:48:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.35,1:48:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲要守护的...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.60,1:48:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.93,1:48:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而是万物生生不息
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.22,1:51:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舅舅
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.43,1:51:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,莲花峰已经封不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.43,1:51:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.43,1:51:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是天崩地裂
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.56,1:51:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沉香
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.56,1:51:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你母亲守护的是世间安宁
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.43,1:51:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是金霞洞
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.26,1:51:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,去劈开山吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.43,1:52:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.97,1:52:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.85,1:53:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.76,1:53:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.56,1:53:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.89,1:53:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.35,1:53:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你都这么大了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.89,1:53:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.43,1:53:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.68,1:54:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.68,1:54:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.81,1:54:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.10,1:54:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还得有劳你照顾他了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.72,1:55:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.35,1:55:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.60,1:55:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我会和玄鸟一起
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.18,1:55:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,守护世间
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.26,1:55:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,守护你
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.85,1:55:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.06,1:55:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.26,1:55:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.81,1:55:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.02,1:55:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.97,1:55:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.89,1:55:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.64,1:56:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...为什么...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.10,1:56:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲早已和玄鸟之气化为一体
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.68,1:56:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,华山劈开了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.10,1:56:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,玄鸟飞去
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.18,1:56:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她也随之而去了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.56,1:56:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有你在
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.06,1:56:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有这世间万物在
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.89,1:56:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她会回来的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.06,2:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,齐天大圣出了水帘洞
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.35,2:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抬眼一看
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.56,2:02:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好一位玉面郎君
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.27,2:02:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,此人正是玉帝的亲外甥
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.27,2:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当年
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.22,2:02:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,斧劈桃山 力降玄鸟的二郎神
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.02,2:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,杨戬 杨戬 他怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.60,2:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊这 他这就走啦啊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.10,2:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,二郎神好厉害啊!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.56,2:02:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你打不过杨戬啊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.64,2:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是一故事
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.35,2:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.43,2:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.89,2:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.56,2:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一为迁客去长沙
Dialogue: 0,2:03:12.56,2:03:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,西望长安不见家
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.56,2:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,黄鹤楼中吹玉笛
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.43,2:03:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,江城五月落梅花
